"모카","body":"맞아. 빵! 근처에 맛있는\n빵집이 있단 말이지~\n지금 가볼래? 엥, 그건 아니라고?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"episode025-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"안 넘어가네~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"niyaniya01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"episode025-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"우리 음악?\n뭐~ 한마디로 「이모션」하지~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"eeto01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"episode025-007","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"「이모션」이 뭔지 모르겠다고?\n모르나~? 뭐 그렇구나~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":7,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":7,"voiceId":"episode025-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":7}],"windowDisplayName":"모카","body":"음, 뭐라고 해야 하나.\n좋은 느낌이라고 할까~","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motion